c\",\"url\":\"/property/article/329392/The-Pavilia-Farm-III-records-over-38-times-oversubscription-on-Wednesday\",\"redirect_url\":null,\"title\":\"The Pavilia Farm III records over 38 times oversubscription on Wednesday\",\"digest\":\"The Pavilia Farm III in Tai Wai, co-developed by New World Development (0017) and MTR Corporation (0066), has received more than 3,500 checks so far, marking over 38 times oversubscription of the 88 units.\",\"channel_rect\":{\"background_color\":\"C90027\",\"icon\":null,\"name\":\"Property\",\"url\":\"/property\"},\"channel_name\":\"Property\",\"channel_url\":\"/property\",\"video_id\":\"\",\"video_path\":\"\",\"video_title\":\"\",\"video_cover_img\":\"\",\"video_duration\":null,\"publish_at\":1776244925,\"updated_at\":1776244925,\"live_id\":null,\"m3u8_live_url\":null,\"byline\":[]},{\"article_id\":\"329372\",\"key_image\":{\"alt_text\":\"The Center.\",\"caption\":\"The Center.\",\"src\":\"https://image.hkstandard.com.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/17c6a51a721f6bd008c3be9923a2cf4f/2026-04/PY251201BUILDING014.JPG\",\"srcset\":\"https://image.hkstandard.com.hk/f/1920p0/0x0/100/none/1ccc964372e8c1f8667c7af664683e67/2026-04/PY251201BUILDING014.JPG 1920w,https://image.hkstandard.com.hk/f/1440p0/0x0/100/none/94d15ea8ab36a2951e310bf000a4cafb/2026-04/PY251201BUILDING014.JPG 1440w,https://image.hkstandard.com.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/17c6a51a721f6bd008c3be9923a2cf4f/2026-04/PY251201BUILDING014.JPG 1024w,https://image.hkstandard.com.hk/f/640p0/0x0/100/none/b356f94625c86d07eeebc795527eb569/2026-04/PY251201BUILDING014.JPG 640w\"},\"article_type\":\"basic\",\"url\":\"/property/article/329372/DBS-Hong-Kong-to-buy-six-more-floors-at-The-Center-for-26m\",\"redirect_url\":null,\"title\":\"DBS Hong Kong to buy six more floors at The Center for $2.6m\",\"digest\":\"DBS Bank (Hong Kong) said on Wednesday that it planned to buy six additional floors at The Center in Central for HK$2.62 billion, marking the biggest deal in the city's commercial property market this year.\",\"channel_rect\":{\"background_color\":\"C90027\",\"icon\":null,\"name\":\"Property\",\"url\":\"/property\"},\"channel_name\":\"Property\",\"channel_url\":\"/property\",\"video_id\":\"\",\"video_path\":\"\",\"video_title\":\"\",\"video_cover_img\":\"\",\"video_duration\":null,\"publish_at\":1776237950,\"updated_at\":1776237950,\"live_id\":null,\"m3u8_live_url\":null,\"byline\":[\"Helen Zhong\"]},{\"article_id\":\"329268\",\"key_image\":{\"alt_text\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"src\":\"https://image.hkstandard.com.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/34d5333a3fe8afd0b4d38bbb916dd8a6/2026-04/PH260412PH16.jpg\",\"srcset\":\"https://image.hkstandard.com.hk/f/1920p0/0x0/100/none/08db8cb500b9857e27feb5e4396c5c64/2026-04/PH260412PH16.jpg 1920w,https://image.hkstandard.com.hk/f/1440p0/0x0/100/none/e95f0609a52396c1ec1e2885a973b948/2026-04/PH260412PH16.jpg 1440w,https://image.hkstandard.com.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/34d5333a3fe8afd0b4d38bbb916dd8a6/2026-04/PH260412PH16.jpg 1024w,https://image.hkstandard.com.hk/f/640p0/0x0/100/none/cfbb5de2e264dfbef161bb7d8de13e59/2026-04/PH260412PH16.jpg 640w\"},\"article_type\":\"basic\",\"url\":\"/property/article/329268/The-Pavilia-Farm-III-releases-price-list-of-38-units-on-Tuesday\",\"redirect_url\":null,\"title\":\"The Pavilia Farm III releases price list of 38 units on Tuesday\",\"digest\":\"The Pavilia Farm III in Tai Wai, co-developed by New World Development (0017) and MTR Corporation (0066), uploaded the latest price list of 38 units on Tuesday, with discounted prices ranging from HK$7.55 million to HK$12.60 million.\",\"channel_rect\":{\"background_color\":\"C90027\",\"icon\":null,\"name\":\"Property\",\"url\":\"/property\"},\"channel_name\":\"Property\",\"channel_url\":\"/property\",\"video_id\":\"\",\"video_path\":\"\",\"video_title\":\"\",\"video_cover_img\":\"\",\"video_duration\":null,\"publish_at\":1776157907,\"updated_at\":1776157907,\"live_id\":null,\"m3u8_live_url\":null,\"byline\":[]},{\"article_id\":\"329257\",\"key_image\